title: Cylum's SNES ROM Set (2014)
description:
This torrent contains the following folders/files:


- [Europe] 60 files - Games that were exclusive to Europe.

- [Japan] 30 files - Some of the better Japan only games that never got a USA/Europe release. Does not contain games that are in the 'Translations' folder.

- [Prototypes] 47 files - Prototypes/Betas for unreleased games from all regions.

- [ROM Hacks] 23 files - A collection of some of the best ROM Hacks available.

- [Translations] 145 files - Complete or near complete English translations for games released in Europe/Japan.

- [Unlicensed] 18 files - Unlicensed games that were released on cartridge.

- Game Titles #-Z (720 files) - Complete USA ROM set. All of the games released in the USA.

- snes9x-1.53 (32 & 64 bit versions) - Emulator


All of the titles were renamed to their official title name that's on the box art. Removed all of the GoodTools/NoIntro, etc. tags (can be easily restored using a rom mananger and specific data files). All roms have been tested to make sure they're working/clean dumps. All the games are archived in their own individual zip folder.

This is an update to my previously uploaded "Complete SNES Rom Set (NA/EU) + More)" torrent.
